# Privacy Policy

**Last updated: April 2026**

## Overview

Compute Rush: Idle Clicker is a free idle game. We do not collect, store, or share any personal data directly.

## Advertising

This app displays ads via **Google AdMob**. AdMob may collect device identifiers and usage data to serve personalised advertising. This is governed by Google's privacy policy:

[https://policies.google.com/privacy](https://policies.google.com/privacy)

## Data We Collect

We do not collect, transmit, or store any personal data. No account registration is required to play.

Game progress is saved locally on your device only.

